    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project car or a bare-bones runner? This vehicle is priced to reflect its poor condition \u2014 it has significant wear, cosmetic damage, and mechanical issues that will need attention. It's an honest fixer-upper opportunity for the handy buyer or someone who needs basic transportation and is ready to put in some work. What you see is what you get, and at this price, there's real value for the right buyer willing to roll up their sleeves!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
